{{!
  CHARGEN CUSTOM CONTENT SNIPPET

  Adds the Secret and Goal form fields to the chargen process.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom.hbs

  STEP 1: Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom.hbs

  STEP 2: Find the <div class="tab-content"> that contains the other tab panes
  (you should see Demographics, Groups, Abilities, Background, etc. as <div class="tab-pane">)

  STEP 3: Copy the <div class="tab-pane"> block below and paste it at the END,
  just before the closing </div> tag of tab-content:

  ---START COPY HERE---
  <div class="tab-pane fade active show" id="chargen-inklings-pane">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="chargen-secret-title">Secret - Title</label>
      {{input id="chargen-secret-title" type="text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_title placeholder="A short title for your secret"}}
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="chargen-secret-text">Secret - Description</label>
      {{textarea id="chargen-secret-text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_text placeholder="Describe an IC secret your character holds..." rows=4}}
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="chargen-goal-title">Goal - Title</label>
      {{input id="chargen-goal-title" type="text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_title placeholder="A short title for your goal"}}
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="chargen-goal-text">Goal - Description</label>
      {{textarea id="chargen-goal-text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_text placeholder="Describe what your character is working toward..." rows=4}}
    </div>
  </div>
  ---END COPY---

  IMPORTANT DETAILS:

  ACTIVE CLASS:
  - The tab-pane has classes="fade active show" so it displays on page load
  - If you want it to NOT be the active tab on load, remove "active show"

  ID MATCHING:
  - The id="chargen-inklings-pane" MUST match the href in chargen-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs
  - Do NOT change this value

  PLACEMENT:
  - This <div class="tab-pane"> must go INSIDE the <div class="tab-content">
  - It should be at the same level as Demographics, Groups, Abilities, etc.
  - Paste it at the END, just before </div> closes the tab-content

  FORM FIELDS:
  - This creates 4 fields: secret title, secret text, goal title, goal text
  - These correspond to the field names in chargen-custom.snippet.js
  - If you prefer rich text editing, swap the <textarea> elements for a markdown editor

  FIELD NAMES:
  - inkling_secret_title, inkling_secret_text, inkling_goal_title, inkling_goal_text
  - These names MUST match exactly what chargen-custom.snippet.js sends

  IF YOU CUSTOMIZED chargen_required_types:
  If your game uses different inkling types (e.g., chargen_required_types: [hooks]),
  rename the fields accordingly. Example for single "hooks" type:

  BEFORE (secret and goal):
    {{input ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_title ...}}
    {{textarea ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_text ...}}
    {{input ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_title ...}}
    {{textarea ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_text ...}}

  AFTER (hooks only):
    {{input ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_hooks_title ...}}
    {{textarea ... value=this.char.custom.inkling_hooks_text ...}}

  The pattern is: this.char.custom.inkling_{type}_title and inkling_{type}_text
  Also update the labels and placeholders to match your custom types.
}}
